Calendula is developed by the Research Centre for Information Technologies of the USC (CITIUS) 

Visit our web site for more info: 
citius.usc.es/calendula 

Calendula is an open source project. You can contribute with ideas or suggestions through our Github page or by sending an e-mail to us: 
https://github.com/citiususc/calendula 
citius.calendula@usc.es 

For this development, we use several open source libraries that are shown below:

AboutLibraries is a library to offer you all the information you need of your libraries! 

Most modern apps feature an Used Library-Section and for this some information of those libs is required. As it gets annoying to copy those strings always to your app I have developed this small helper library to provide the required information.
